data.description: Motivated Seller! Welcome to Carlisle Creek Condos, a gated community! Enter into heated tile floor. Spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and wood burning fireplace surrounded by granite. Lavish Kitchen Features Stainless Appliances, Under Mount Sink, Granite Counter Tops, Tile Back Splash, & Friendly Eating Bar. Separate dining area by sliders offers ample natural light. Sliding door accesses balcony deck with additional storage closet. Bathroom with heated tile floors, custom vanity with quartz counter tops, and tiled shower. TWO assigned parking spaces, one covered and one uncovered. Community club house features billiards, media & weight room, & outdoor pool. Close to Boeing, parks & convenient access to I-5 & 405. NO RENTAL CAP!
